# Naming conventions for Dev::Deps

**Repository subclasses**: `<Thing>Repository` — e.g. `GitRepository`,
`UrlRepository`, `BrewRepository`. Not `Registry`, `Source`, `Adapter`.

**Integration subclasses**: `<Thing>Integration` — e.g. `CmakeIntegration`,
`BrewIntegration`.

**Lockfile API**: `lock` verb to write, `read` to get all deps back.
No `write`, no `lockfile_path` params — routing is internal.
